==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hatcher
<hw>Hatch"er</hw> <pr>(-⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who hatches, or that which hatches; a hatching apparatus; an
incubator.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who contrives or originates; a
plotter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A great <qex>hatcher</qex> and breeder of business.</q>
<rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hatchery</ent>⟦br⟧
